[RULES]
1. No Torches.
2. No Manual horizontal mining.
	you can dig quarries by hand but not branch mines or tunnels.
	you are allowed to go caving for ores.
3. No reseting your spawn.
	you can use a bed to make it day but you must break and store it afterwards.
4. No Teleportation of items/energy.
5. No powered flight.
	falling does not count as flight. (hang gliders are ok)
6. No Quarries in the overworld.
7. Set config for no infinite water

[GOALS]
	1,000,000,000 (1 billion) diamonds
	full manny tool set from Tcon
	Full Research completion in Thaumcraft
	Fully functional and populated city

